    Graph<EdgeImpl<I>,​VertexImpl<I>,​I,​java.lang.Double>
    public class GraphImpl<I>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Graph<EdgeImpl<I>,​VertexImpl<I>,​I,​java.lang.Double>
    General oriented simple graph class. Uses EdgeImpl as its edges and VertexImpl as its vertices. Provides methods for parsing a graph from a file in 3 modes: A for adjacency matrix I for incidence matrix L for adjacency lists; and for topological sort. Adjacency matrix should look like:
